scripts.compile: npm run compile:win && npm run compile:lin
scripts.compile:win: node -e "if (process.platform === 'win32') process.exit(1)" || , if exist dist rmdir /Q /S dist && tsc && tsc --build tsconfig.es5.json
scripts.compile:lin: node -e "if (process.platform !== 'win32') process.exit(1)" || rm -rf dist && tsc && tsc --build tsconfig.es5.json
